{
  "stem": "19218.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 342.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I'm going to look for the gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "When we heard this, you know, bread for the first time in six days, five days, bread, a piece of bread, whatever they gave us, and we would swallow it in seconds.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And-- and we knew that what-- what he told her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were ready to go away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She says no, wait, wait, wait, that she would bring out more bread and more bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "In about five minutes, we must have each had I don't know how much bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But we had bread and water too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he says to her, everybody escaped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There's no-- there's no authority in the city left anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "All the gendarmes are gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "All the police, militia, is gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The Americans are three kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he mentioned the town, which I don't know what it was, the little city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Of course, we heard this, so that Nazi German says still to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Look, he says, you're in no position to walk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "You can't walk, he says.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So we're going to do something for you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "This morning, he says, there was a international prisoners of war here, a whole group of them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And they were walking in that direction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I know that you can't walk, so we'll put you on a horse and cart, he says.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And one of us will drive you there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Fine, we don't have to walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "International prisoners, I figured that's a little bit better than inmates from concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We immediately got a hold of some clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] When they put us on this wagon, there were two other guys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Probably the same as us, but nobody would talk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And he had some clothes there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "These guys had some clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "We took the clothes from him.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
